{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore asteroids and extract their gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_dirt_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/vertical_camera_level_scroll.gif?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_dirt_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TIME = DIFFICULTY!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The longer you stay on an asteroid, the faster enemies will spawn, and the more threatening they'll be. You'll need to stay for a while though, because your\u00a0<span class=\"bb_strike\">evil</span> employer won't let you live if you don't meet your quota! If you really want to excel, try exceeding your quota so you can buy even more upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/exploding_a_bunch_of_enemies.gif?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_stone_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UPGRADES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your gold to buy unique stackable items! Every item is satisfying to use, and quite impactful. Try out combinations of items to find powerful synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_items.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_stone_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STAT BUFFS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can also use your hard-earned gold to improve your stats. These stat buffs aren't typically as strong as items, but they're still important for any asteroid miner. (aka comet rogue)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/shop_items_closeup.gif?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_mud_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FULLY DESTRUCTIBLE PROCEDURALLY-GENERATED ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level is procedurally-generated and fully destructible. There are various traps and treasures to be found!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/barrel_chain_reaction.gif?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_mud_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNLOCKABLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you die, your gold is automatically put towards unlocking new weapons and pets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_weapons.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_pets.gif?t=1737765619\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252310/extras/description_obsidian_border.png?t=1737765619\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLEASE WISHLIST THE GAME, I'M POOR!!! D:</h2